#

Creamy Tuscan Garlic Chicken with Spinach and Sun-Dried Tomatoes

$15
600 kcal
Difficulty: 30%
Servings: 2

Allergens:

DairyChicken

Dietary Tags:

High ProteinLow Carb

Tags:

EasyComfort FoodDinner

Description

A rich and creamy chicken dish infused with garlic, paired with fresh spinach and tangy sun-dried tomatoes for a delightful meal.

Ingredients

  • Chicken breasts: 2 pieces
  • Heavy cream: 1 cup
  • Garlic: 4 cloves, minced
  • Fresh spinach: 3 cups
  • Sun-dried tomatoes: 1/2 cup, chopped
  • Olive oil: 2 tablespoons
  • Italian seasoning: 1 teaspoon
  • Parmesan cheese: 1/2 cup, grated
  • Salt: to taste
  • Black pepper: to taste
